    dc:date "2013" ;
    dc:title "A new marine vertebrate assemblage from the Late Neogene Purisima Formation in Central California, part II: Pinnipeds and Cetaceans" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4538243>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4538233>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4538245>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4538229>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4538241>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4538231>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4538237>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4538247> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4538243>
    dc:description "FIG. 16. — Possible taphonomic pathway of the holotype specimen of Balaenoptera bertae n. sp.: A, death; B, initial decay,bloat, and floating; C, advanced skeletonization of the facial region and loss of rostral elements; D, continued skeletonization of the facial region and the loss of petrotympanics and mandibles; E, loss of the cranium from the carcass; F, arrival of the skull on the seafloor in the ventral-up position; G, collapse and rotation of the vomer and frontals and contact with the seafloor; H, burial; I, diagenetic compaction and fracturing of basicranial elements; J, formation of a concretion during later diagenesis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4538243/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4538233>
    dc:description "FIG. 13. — Holotype cranium of Balaenoptera bertae n. sp., UCMP 219078,in lateral view: A, photograph; B, interpretive line drawing. Cross hatching denotes broken or missing bone, and gray denotes adhering matrix. Scale bar: 10 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4538233/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4538245>
    dc:description "FIG. 17. — Reconstruction of the skull of Balaenoptera bertae n. sp.; A, lateral view; B, ventral view; C, dorsal view. Scale bar: 20 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4538245/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4538229>
    dc:description "FIG. 11. — Holotype cranium of Balaenoptera bertae n. sp., UCMP 21907, in dorsal view: A, photograph; B, interpretive line drawing. Cross hatching denotes broken or missing bone, and gray denotes adhering matrix. Scale bar: 10 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4538229/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4538241>
    dc:description "FIG. 15. — Holotype skull of Balaenoptera bertae n. sp., UCMP 219078: A, skull in posterodorsal view; B, right auditory region in ventral view; C, left auditory region in ventral view. Left paroccipital process is complete, but obscured by plaster display cradle. Scale bars: 10 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4538241/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4538231>
    dc:description "FIG. 12. — Holotype cranium of Balaenoptera bertae n. sp., UCMP 21907, in ventral view:A, photograph; B, interpretive line drawing. Cross hatching denotes broken or missing bone, and gray denotes adhering matrix. Scale bar: 10 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4538231/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4538237>
    dc:description "FIG. 14. — Vertex of holotype cranium of Balaenoptera bertae n. sp., UCMP 219078: A, dorsal view of vertex; B, interpretive line drawing. Gray color denotes matrix, and cross-hatching represents damaged or missing bone. Scale bar: 10 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4538237/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4538247>
    dc:description "FIG. 18. — Strict consensus tree of the phylogenetic analysis executed, including Balaenoptera bertae n. sp. within the data matrix of Marx (2011). Basal parts of the tree outside the Caperea + Balaenopteroidea clade are not shown; support values are Bremer support and GC frequency values. †, denotes extinct taxa." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4538247/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

